  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="date">Last updated: May 30, 2025</p>

  <p>This Privacy Policy describes Our policies and procedures on the collection, use and disclosure of Your information when You use the Service and tells You about Your privacy rights and how the law protects You.</p>
  <p>We use Your Personal data to provide and improve the Service. By using the Service, You agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this Privacy Policy.</p>

  <h2>Interpretation and Definitions</h2>
  <h3>Interpretation</h3>
  <p>Words with capital letters have specific meanings. These meanings apply whether the words are used in singular or plural.</p>

  <h3>Definitions</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Account</strong>: A unique account created for You to access our Service.</li>
    <li><strong>Affiliate</strong>: An entity that controls or is controlled by the Company.</li>
    <li><strong>Application</strong>: Refers to CoreStudyWAI.</li>
    <li><strong>Company</strong>: CoreStudyWAI (also "We", "Us", "Our").</li>
    <li><strong>Country</strong>: Maharashtra, India</li>
    <li><strong>Device</strong>: Any device such as a computer, phone, or tablet used to access the Service.</li>
    <li><strong>Personal Data</strong>: Information relating to an identified individual.</li>
    <li><strong>Service</strong>: The CoreStudyWAI application.</li>
    <li><strong>Service Provider</strong>: Third-party entities that process data on behalf of the Company.</li>
    <li><strong>Usage Data</strong>: Data collected automatically during use of the Service.</li>
    <li><strong>You</strong>: The individual or entity accessing the Service.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Collecting and Using Your Personal Data</h2>
  <h3>Types of Data Collected</h3>

  <h4>Personal Data</h4>
  <p>While using Our Service, we may ask for:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Email address</li>
    <li>First and last name</li>
    <li>Usage Data</li>
  </ul>

  <h4>Usage Data</h4>
  <p>This includes IP address, browser type, pages visited, and diagnostic data. On mobile, it may also include device ID, OS version, and mobile browser type.</p>

  <h3>Use of Your Personal Data</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>To provide and maintain the Service</li>
    <li>To manage Your Account</li>
    <li>To perform a contract</li>
    <li>To contact You (emails, calls, push notifications)</li>
    <li>To provide news, offers, and information unless opted out</li>
    <li>To manage Your requests</li>
    <li>For business transfers or reorganizations</li>
    <li>For data analysis and service improvement</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Sharing Your Personal Data</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>With Service Providers</li>
    <li>For business transfers</li>
    <li>With Affiliates</li>
    <li>With Business Partners</li>
    <li>With Other Users in public areas</li>
    <li>With Your consent</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Retention of Your Personal Data</h3>
  <p>We keep Personal Data only as long as necessary for legal and service-related purposes. Usage Data may be kept longer if needed for analytics or legal reasons.</p>

  <h3>Transfer of Your Personal Data</h3>
  <p>Data may be transferred to and stored in locations with different data protection laws. We ensure reasonable safeguards are in place.</p>

  <h3>Delete Your Personal Data</h3>
  <p>You can request deletion of your data via account settings or by contacting us at <a href="mailto:corestudywai@gmail.com">corestudywai@gmail.com</a>.</p>

  <h3>Disclosure of Your Personal Data</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Business Transactions</strong>: Your data may be transferred during company restructuring.</li>
    <li><strong>Law Enforcement</strong>: Data may be disclosed if required by law.</li>
    <li><strong>Other Legal Requirements</strong>: To protect rights, investigate misuse, or respond to legal obligations.</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Security of Your Personal Data</h3>
  <p>We strive to protect Your data but cannot guarantee 100% security.</p>

  <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>We do not knowingly collect data from children under 13. If you believe a child has shared data, please contact us.</p>

